Nexus Platform plugin

Configure the plugin
Manage Jenkins->configure system->Sonatype Nexus
Display Name: Nexus Server
ServerID: Nexus Server
Server URL: http://19.195.82.81:8081/
Credentials:Provide the Nexus server credentials

Create an item - maven project
Fill the Git repository and build package steps
In section Nexus Repository Manager Publisher
Nexus Instance: Instance that nexus is configured will populate here.
Nexus Repository: <whatever the repository created in nexus server>
Group:<Package name followed by Project>
Artifact: <name of the artifact>
Version: Version number to be updated in artifact
Packaging: packaging type.
Maven Artifact: place where the maven built artifacts are stored.



